Sinatra-SDB is an implementation of the Amazon SimpleDB API.  Based on the
Parkplace, written by _why, Sinatra-SDB provide full '2007-11-07' and '2009-4-15' 
versions API interface. Sinatra-SDB use SQL DB(with ActiveRecord) sotre Data,now.


Install
------------------------------------------------------------------

We could install from github

  git clone git://github.com/tangtao/sinatra-sdb.git
  cd sinatra-sdb/
  cp sinatra-sdb.yml.example sinatra-sdb.yml
  bundle install
  rake db:migrate


Setup
------------------------------------------------------------------

Once Sinatra-SDB has been installed we can start our server

  rackup -p 7000

